lexicon = 
  heat, poke, red, sit, yam, gawk, lag, tim, doop, back

Default State:
  yam: change to windows state
  poke: change to launching state
  tim: change focus
  red: close window (not implemented)
  doop: change to browsing state
  back: change to default store
Windows State:
  poke: change to launching state
  sit: snap left
  tim: minimize window
  gok: snap right
  doop: unminimize window
  back: change to default store
Launching State:
  poke: change to launching state
  heat: launch Firefox
  gok: launch terminal
  red: launch itunes
  sit: display itunes song
  lag: play/pause itunes
  tim: next itunes song
  back: change to default store
Brwosing State:
  yam: press f
  poke: change to launching state
  sit: press 2
  tim: press 1
  lag: press enter
  red: press 0
  heat: go to favorite
  back: change to default store

